    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00b0C/ 180\u00b0C (fan)/ 390\u00b0F/ Gas 6</p> <p>Put a large baking tray (or two) in the oven to heat up (this will stop the pizza bottoms from going soggy!)</p> <p>Add the\u00a0<strong>tomato paste</strong>\u00a0and <strong>dried oregano</strong> to a bowl with a generous pinch of\u00a0<strong>salt</strong>,\u00a0<strong>pepper</strong>\u00a0and\u00a0<strong>sugar</strong></p> <p>Add 5 tbsp\u00a0<span class=\"text-danger\">[10 tbsp]</span><strong>\u00a0cold water</strong>\u00a0and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your\u00a0<strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Trim the ends from the <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong>, then finely slice</p> <p>Chop the <strong>smoked bacon</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain and pat the\u00a0<strong>mozzarella</strong>\u00a0dry with\u00a0<strong>kitchen paper</strong>\u00a0(squeeze as much liquid out as you can!)</p> <p>Tear the\u00a0<strong>drained mozzarella</strong>\u00a0into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong>\u00a0pizza bases</strong>\u00a0to a baking tray (or two)</p> <p>Divide the\u00a0<strong>tomato sauce\u00a0</strong>between the\u00a0<strong>pizza bases\u00a0</strong>and spread it evenly all over them with the back of a spoon</p> <p>Top with the<strong>\u00a0torn mozzarella </strong>and\u00a0dot the<strong> onion marmalade </strong>all over</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Top with the <strong>sliced Brussels sprouts</strong> and <strong>chopped bacon</strong></p> <p>Season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Put the tray in the oven for 13-15 min or until the cheese has melted and the bases are crisp \u2013 these are your <strong>Christmas bacon &amp; sprout pizzas</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> and <strong>mayonnaise</strong> in a bowl \u2013 this is your<strong> mustard mayo</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong>\u00a0Christmas bacon &amp; sprout pizzas</strong> with the<strong> mustard mayo</strong> to the side</p> <p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
